name: Neon & Swan A4 Print Set
description:
The dynamic synth duo; Anais Neon and Martin Swan of the band Vile Electrodes appear in a very limited run of digital art based on original watercolour illustrations by Lucida Whisk aka 'Whisk82'.

Each set contains two A4 art board prints; one of Neon in illuminated winged helmet and the other of Swan as a rabbit/vicar, fine stage attire you will agree. 

Measuring approx. 21 x 30 cm each, they will make any wall instantly stunning in a pair of 18 x 14 inch frames. 

Run of 25 pairs; signed and numbered by the artist on the reverse. 
Printed on earth-friendly 300gsm recycled art board, carefully and securely packaged in a durable hardbacked envelope.

+++PLUS+++ Bonus whisk82 artwork with every order! +++

*See Terms and Conditions page (link below) for details on print specifications, payment and shipping.
